  <TermName>systemic therapy</TermName>
  <TermPronunciation>(sis-TEH-mik THAYR-uh-pee)</TermPronunciation>
  <TermDefinition>
    <DefinitionText>Treatment using substances that travel through the bloodstream, reaching and affecting cells all over the body.</DefinitionText>
    <Dictionary>Cancer.gov</Dictionary>
    <Audience>Patient</Audience>
  </TermDefinition>
